An '''unknown [[governor]]-general''' was installed over [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] following the ouster of [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]] in [[28 ABY/Legends|28 ABY]], during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

Sometime after the end of the war in [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]], the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] removed the governor-general from Corellia as a reward for the system supporting the Alliance's war effort. The position was replaced with that of [[Five World Prime Minister]], of whom the first was [[Aidel Saxan]].

